title: My.Dream.Home.s02e08.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description:
Having lived in four houses in four years and now crammed into a tiny apartment, Marianne and Steve crave a high-end house to call home. Real estate and renovation experts, Property Brothers Drew and Jonathan Scott, come to the rescue and help the couple find a budget-friendly dream home that can be renovated on time. With a budget that doesn't match the couple's expectations, Drew and Jonathan struggle to sell the potential of a fixer-upper. The couple has to decide between two big renovation projects so the brothers' design equally tantalizing plans for both. One favours Steve's top-of-the-line kitchen fantasy, while the other caters to Marianne's vision of a master bedroom retreat. The couple makes a tough decision but from the first hammer swing, disaster strikes and everyone worries that the ultimate dream renovation has become the ultimate nightmare.
If you see "Hector" on the end of a file it means I capped it.
Enjoy, Gaz/Hector :)
